Author: cherrynuts
Text: might be a little cliche, but maybe try incorporating a large quantity of green leaf vegetables in your diet. before removing anything, it's a very good step to take... just something that's rung true for me in my life :)

Author: Squeakymeeper13
Text: Hey lovely, carbs are a necessary thing.  No stress, deep breathes.  Even if you ate the entire package with a gallon of butter, your weight will still be back to normal in a few days.   It's okay.  You got this.
